 Development Log – Pennywise

This log documents the day-to-day progress of building the Pennywise personal budget tracker. Entries include planning decisions, technical setups, design adjustments, and coding milestones.

---

 July 14, 2025 – Day 1

Tasks Completed:
- Finalized project name: Pennywise
- Defined app concept and main feature set
- Outlined initial visual layout for the Home screen
- Chose core technologies (React, Tailwind, Chart.js)
- Created project icon and app branding direction
- Set up GitHub repository and began documentation
- Created initial README with concept, stack, features, and status

Next Steps:
- Finalize prerequisite installations (Node, Vite, Tailwind)
- Scaffold folder structure for React project
- Begin building the Home screen layout
